{"4294210": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Date the Difference", "steam_appid": 4294210, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/cadd919d304a287b4890ae153134387d.poster.avif?t=1771360357\" aria-label=\"找出差異。 感受連結。\" width=1170 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/cadd919d304a287b4890ae153134387d.webm?t=1771360357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/cadd919d304a287b4890ae153134387d.mp4?t=1771360357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Date the Difference》是一款風格亮眼的休閒益智遊戲，將經典的「找不同」玩法與輕鬆浪漫的敘事結合在一起。探索精心打造的場景，仔細比對畫面，找出細微差異。每一關都不只是謎題，更是一段瞬間、一場約會，也是更靠近認識迷人角色與他們故事的一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放鬆、專注，享受「觀察力玩法」與「俏皮曖昧」之間的完美平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/d44e85c2e8b0a6145b8189b90d7b3f24.poster.avif?t=1771360357\" aria-label=\"核心玩法\" width=1170 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/d44e85c2e8b0a6145b8189b90d7b3f24.webm?t=1771360357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/d44e85c2e8b0a6145b8189b90d7b3f24.mp4?t=1771360357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spot the Difference - 在兩張圖片中找出不同之處</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >限時關卡，包含星級評分與表現分數</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >縮放、提示與增益道具，應對困難時刻</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多樣化的場景中逐步提升難度</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/e9286308701a68f0473e61d4cfc2988c.poster.avif?t=1771360357\" aria-label=\"約會與劇情\" width=1170 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/e9286308701a68f0473e61d4cfc2988c.webm?t=1771360357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/e9286308701a68f0473e61d4cfc2988c.mp4?t=1771360357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >認識多位角色，每位都有獨特個性</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >輕鬆對話與俏皮調情營造約會氛圍</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨進度解鎖新的場景、圖片與時刻</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集約會中的難忘照片瞬間</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/5ee07dff8dcc02856e44102c89db308c.poster.avif?t=1771360357\" aria-label=\"成長與競爭\" width=1170 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/5ee07dff8dcc02856e44102c89db308c.webm?t=1771360357\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extras/5ee07dff8dcc02856e44102c89db308c.mp4?t=1771360357\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以精準與速度獲得星星與獎勵</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立角色與場景收藏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在排行榜上與其他玩家競爭</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4294210/extra